item.title: Need a Custom Client Made Please!
item.dc:creator: @Vince2 Vince,
item.description:
@Vince2 wrote:

[quote=“foxyfoxx, post:7, topic:372361”][quote author=Vince, link=topic=468411.msg3425512#msg3425512 date=1291884264]

Dude i have no idea how to ? do u think you could help me ?

Either start off with a blank client, experiment, and hope to succeed, or study Java, that’s how I started, more or less studying Java before I’ve even heard of RSPS.
[/quote]

i think you should help me i allready have tried and failed…[/quote]

If you’ve failed already, you probably didn’t even try to study, so yes, you did fail. Try looking up some things on Google, it’ll help you get more advanced in Java period, people think Java is RuneScape, which it’s not, it’s actually the other way around.
